## A Closure with Conditional Forwarding

A closure that routes incoming values to one of two accumulators based on a predicate, so you can split a stream into two buckets.

```scheme
;; A splitter that routes values to one of two accumulators based on a predicate.
(define make-splitter
  (lambda (pred?)
    (let ((true-bucket '())
          (false-bucket '()))
      (lambda (values)
        (for-each
          (lambda (v)
            (if (pred? v)
                (set! true-bucket (cons v true-bucket))
                (set! false-bucket (cons v false-bucket))))
          values)
        (list 'true (reverse true-bucket) 'false (reverse false-bucket))))))

(define splitter (make-splitter even?))

